            <title>[SOLR-5866] UpdateShardHandler needs to use the system default scheme registry to properly handle https via javax.net.ssl.* properties</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-5866</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The UpdateShardHandler configures it&apos;s own PoolingClientConnectionManager which &lt;b&gt;doesn&apos;t&lt;/b&gt; use the system default scheme registry factory which interrogates the javax.net.ssl.* system properties to wire up the https scheme into HttpClient. To ease configuration the system default registry should be used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
